Name: GetProfile
Tagline: User profiles and long-term memory for your AI agents
Description: Self-hosted and open-source user profiles and long-term memory for your AI agents. Unlike generic memory solutions that store blobs of text, GetProfile extracts natural language summary, typed traits with confidence scores and relevant memories with importance levels into a structured user profiles stored in your own PostgreSQL database.

Name: Sparkle
Tagline: Simplified cold email outreach
Description: Sparkle offers robust email deliverability in a box. Skip domain setup, creating accounts, and managing deliverability so you can run campaigns with verified leads to grow your business. Pay-as-you-go, starting at $4 per 1000 emails sent.

Name: Touched Grass
Tagline: Show the world you’ve touched grass
Description: Did you touch grass today? Shipped something? Did some marketing? Touched sand instead? Create a badge for your achievement and share it everywhere.

Name: MiMo-V2-Flash
Tagline: Ultra-fast 309B MoE model for coding & agents
Description: MiMo-V2-Flash is a 309B MoE (15B active) model by Xiaomi. It is a powerful, efficient, and ultra-fast foundation language model that particularly excels in reasoning, coding, and agentic scenarios, while also serving as an excellent general-purpose assistant for everyday tasks.

Name: MyLens for Chrome
Tagline: Your AI visualization partner, right in your browser.
Description: MyLens is your AI visualization partner for the entire web. Wherever you are browsing—YouTube, websites, docs, news, etc— click MyLens. it analyzes the content, pulls out the key insights and turns them into an AI visualization. Every element is clickable and source-linked, so you can trust what you’re seeing and jump straight to the exact part you need. Need it in another language? Just ask—MyLens supports 60+ languages. If you skim a lot of content online, MyLens will save you a ton of time.

Name: MARINOVA
Tagline: See the Ocean in Real Time
Description: Marinova is a real-time ocean intelligence platform that turns live marine and climate data into clear, interactive visualizations. We help researchers, policymakers, and climate innovators monitor ocean conditions, detect risks early, and make data-driven decisions. Think of Marinova as a live dashboard for the ocean, built for impact, clarity, and action.

Name: Cleanly – WP Cleaning Booking Software
Tagline: Smart booking software for cleaning businesses inside WP
Description: Cleanly is an all-in-one booking system for cleaning businesses. Manage bookings, staff, payments, locations, reviews, and pricing from one dashboard. Built for house cleaning, maid services, and growing cleaning companies.

Name: Origo | Vibe Build Things
Tagline: Create parametric 3d designs using natural language.
Description: Design 3D models with natural language. No CAD experience required.

Name: Star Sailors
Tagline: Contribute to science by playing games
Description: Star Sailors is a browser-based citizen science game where you explore space using real astronomical data. Deploy a virtual telescope, discover and customise exoplanets, track weather systems, and hunt asteroids and comets. Learn scientific methods by doing, contribute to real research, and collaborate with other citizen scientists — no scientific background required.

Name: CargoLab
Tagline: Free 3d cargo load planner & optimizer
Description: Logistics Software is Broken for the "Little Guys" If you are a giant logistics corporation, you can afford expensive, enterprise-grade B2B software that costs thousands of dollars a year. But if you are a small freight forwarder, an e-commerce startup, or an individual shipper? You are left behind. CargoLab is a free, browser-based 3D Load Planner designed for the rest of us. It brings enterprise-level optimization to everyone, instantly.

Name: Daylight Goals
Tagline: Track your sunlight, now with a 2025 Daylight Recap
Description: Track and optimize your sunlight exposure for better sleep, mood, and overall health with Daylight Goals. And now you can get a GitHub style full year recap of all your time spent outdoors, just by wearing an Apple Watch.

Name: pixelcodeAI
Tagline: the coder of pixel
Description: Pixel Code AI Zero is likely a development environment or a showcase for Generative Pixel Art. The "AI Zero" part of the name suggests a "from-scratch" approach, potentially using AI models (like Neural Cellular Automata or GANs) to grow, evolve, or generate pixel designs without human intervention, or with minimal "code" input

Name: Milky Well Days
Tagline: A calm, simple breast pump & milk tracking app
Description: Milky Well Days is a calm, simple breast pump and milk tracking app built for exhausted parents. Log pumping sessions in seconds, track milk output clearly, and avoid clutter, ads, and subscription pressure. Designed with empathy and minimalism, MilkyWell Days helps you stay consistent without adding stress especially during late nights when simplicity matters most.

Name: Talklet - Now live
Tagline: A place for meaningful conversations, not endless noise
Description: Talklet is a platform for small, topic-based conversations designed for depth, not noise. You create or join focused tables with 2–6 participants around a shared topic and talk live with people who actually want the same conversation. No feeds, no chaos — just real dialogue. After each session, Talklet generates a concise AI-powered summary so insights don’t disappear when the conversation ends.

Name: Cyber-Physics
Tagline: First Kinetic Defense Engine to Stop Zero-DayAttacks offline
Topics: Developer Tools, Artificial Intelligence, GitHub, Security
Description: Traditional AI relies on historical patterns, leaving you vulnerable to Zero-Day attacks. Cyber-Physics introduces a new paradigm: Differential Physics Defense.It treats data streams as physical objects with Mass and Momentum. If a request moves 'too fast' or carries 'too much energy', it's blocked instantly (O(1) complexity) — even if it's never been seen before. Features: 100% Offline (GDPR/Sovereignty compliant). Millisecond response time. Plug-and-play with Splunk, QRadar, and EDRs.

Name: Scaloom
Tagline: The AI agent that earns Reddit trust before promotion
Description: Reddit doesn’t reward promotion — it rewards participation. Scaloom is an AI agent designed to help founders and marketers **earn karma, trust, and visibility the right way** before sharing anything. It discovers relevant subreddits, engages in real discussions with value-first comments, and grows karma steadily without bots, fake upvotes, or rule-breaking. Scaloom helps you unlock posting privileges and turn Reddit into a sustainable growth channel — safely.

Name: Spanning
Tagline: Instantly rewrite resume to match any job description.
Description: Spanning is a purpose-built engine for job seekers to instantly rewrite resume to match any job description.

Name: Name Generator Pro
Tagline: Smart, private AI name generator for anything
Description: Find the perfect name for babies, brands, characters, pets, and more using a 3-tier system: on-device Apple Intelligence and an offline curated engine. Works great on iOS 26+, and still works fully offline on iOS 18 and newer, with no accounts and no data collection.

Name: LazyCalc All-in-One Calculator
Tagline: 5 calculators + converter in one tiny, offline app
Description: 32MB. Perfect for students, shoppers, diners, travelers. 5.0 rating from early users.

Name: Mocksy - GPS Spot Mock for Android
Tagline: Mocking your location with this simple applciation for games
Description: Hey, I am glad to present Mockys the GPS mocking application build for modern Android devices. You can change location with adb command or manually in the app with drag and drop, gps coordinates, zip code, street address, city or country.
